				<LineBreak />
			</Paragraph>

			<Paragraph>
				Feature Inventory Tool 1.2 (FIT 1.2) was deployed last week and can now track patent claim filing. Prior to merging into winmain, all Beta 2 features must have this done.  Please work with your Legal and Corporate Affairs (LCA) contact - the goal is to have all patent claims filed by the end of July.
                <LineBreak />
			</Paragraph>

			<Paragraph>
				<Bold Foreground="Blue">Beta 2 Localization - early notice</Bold>
				<LineBreak />
			</Paragraph>

			<Paragraph>
                We have finalized the localization plans for Beta2.  Beta2 will ship in English, German and Japanese for all SKUs (client/server) as well as Hindi for Starter Edition only. Implementation plans will be finalized over the next 2 weeks with the goal of having a pseudo-loc build available in June. (Note that Beta 1 is English-only.)
                <LineBreak />
			</Paragraph>

